<doc id="32548" wikidata="Q7917139" url="?curid=32548" title="Vaticanus">
<text>Vaticanus may refer to:

* Vatican Hill (in Latin, &quot;Vaticanus Mons&quot;), a location of Holy See
* Vagitanus or Vaticanus, an Etruscan god

